752
00:39:44,300 --> 00:39:45,620
Cuba baring mengiring

753
00:39:46,110 --> 00:39:46,820
atau meniarap.

754
00:39:47,590 --> 00:39:48,390
Dan mungkin kurangkan

755
00:39:48,780 --> 00:39:49,910
