859
00:46:50,180 --> 00:46:50,740
Tidak.

860
00:46:51,910 --> 00:46:52,910
Saya terima.

861
00:46:54,470 --> 00:46:55,870
Saya boleh mula bila-bila masa.

862
00:46:56,390 --> 00:46:57,820
Kami sedang meneliti

