00:47:14,510 --> 00:47:15,620
Biar saya periksa.

873
00:47:15,950 --> 00:47:16,950
Okey, dah hantar.

874
00:47:24,780 --> 00:47:25,660
Pengarah,

875
00:47:26,110 --> 00:47:28,070
Saya rasa saya boleh pujuk dia sertai.

