00:48:49,921 --> 00:48:55,371
♪Aku nampak cahaya bulan dengan jelas♪

894
00:48:56,111 --> 00:49:01,241
♪Menerangi seluruh pintu masuk♪

895
00:49:02,091 --> 00:49:07,561
